    <p>Troubleshooting:</p>
    <p>1. If you have an iPhone and you don&#39;t get a location prompt when you first open the beacon, open your settings app, go to  <strong>Privacy &amp; Security</strong> &gt; <strong>Location Services</strong> &gt; <strong>Safari Websites</strong>, then choose <strong>While Using the App</strong>.</p>
   
